control over my nightmare

13:31.078 --> 13:33.380
at work, last week I posted
a deleted scene from Sing!

13:33.413 --> 13:34.514
Oh.
Clea sings

13:34.547 --> 13:36.316
a Taylor Swift duet
with a pony.
Ooh.

13:36.349 --> 13:37.384
Can't wait to feel
the Twitter love.

13:37.417 --> 13:38.718
(clicks)

13:38.751 --> 13:39.552
This is weird.

13:39.586 --> 13:40.653
What?
I have, like,

13:40.687 --> 13:41.721
a bazillion comments

13:41.754 --> 13:43.390
