14:57.897 --> 14:59.532
crew members sign
non-disclosure agreements.

14:59.566 --> 15:00.700
Oh, please.

15:00.733 --> 15:02.402
Nowadays, you can't
slander someone

15:02.435 --> 15:04.571
in the back of a cab
without it being recorded.

15:04.604 --> 15:06.106
Nothing is private anymore.

15:06.139 --> 15:07.774
