15:09.576 --> 15:11.444
I cannot believe you did this.

15:11.478 --> 15:13.213
I feel extremely violated.

15:13.246 --> 15:15.115
Well, how do you think
the rest of us feel

15:15.148 --> 15:18.651
when you dance like a Vietnamese
kid running across a minefield.

15:18.685 --> 15:21.621
God, these gays
are so... sensitive.

15:26.626 --> 15:29.096
* You nursed me to health
when I had SARS *

15:29.129 --> 15:30.497
(beep, music stops)

15:30.530 --> 15:33.500
* You were on the bed,
I like to please my guy... *

15:33.533 --> 15:35.235
(beep, music stops)

15:35.268 --> 15:39.506
* That's what Rocky calls
